snippet.title: Ethereal: Clash of Souls - Official Pre-Alpha Cinematic
snippet.description:
ETHEREAL: CLASH OF SOULS KICKSTARTER - https://bit.ly/3wJwW3j

The Elders roamed the primordial realm, leaving a path of destruction. The Ethereans joined forces and vanished the Elders to a timeless prison. In Elysium, each Elder must face the other by summoning Myths from throughout the Ether. To escape, they must win. To win, they must fight.
